  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat. Add chorizo and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add red bell pepper and green onion to the skillet, cook for an additional 3-4 minutes or until vegetables are tender.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and cook for another minute until fragrant.",
    "Pour in red wine and bring it to a simmer. Let it reduce slightly, about 2 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and freshly ground black pepper to taste. Serve hot."
